  "body": "The following crashes with \"InternalCompilerError: Invalid conversion to storage type.\" for 0.4.24 and develop.\r\n\r\n```\r\ncontract C {\r\n        uint[] a;\r\n        uint[] b;\r\n        function f() public view {\r\n            uint[] storage c = a;\r\n            uint[] storage d = b;\r\n            d = uint[](c);\r\n        }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe same for base types other than ``uint``.\r\n\r\nFound during #4911.\r\n",
